Great recipe! Moist and chewy. This recipe is easy to modify: 3/4 cup yogurt plus 1/2 cup mashed banana can be subbed for the buttermilk. I always add nuts, coconut and raisens. Coconut increases the level of moisture. If you don't wish to deal with muffin pans, this recipe can be baked in round cake pans and then pie-sliced to serve. Freezes well.

