Rating: 3
These were yummy! Just sweet enough for someone used to sweet muffins. I made my own applesauce, and added diced apples.

Rating: 4
Delicious! I am not a very good cook, but I got tired of buying bran muffins at the store every week, so I decided to try my own. This recipe was easy and turned out perfectly. Baked for exactly 20 min. I used regular sugar and added plumped raisins and 1/2 tsp cinnamon. You can buy wheat bran at a gourmet or health food store in the bulk food isle. Great recipe!

